      • CMD_RETURN_FORCED

        public static final int CMD_RETURN_FORCED
        a subclass to override a method, call superclass this method. need handled return command. Premise in the superclass Java doc has specific requirements. (superclass Java doc: @return CMD (need handle return command)) 
          e.g.
  @Override
  public int onCompletion() {
    //handle return CMD
    if (super.onCompletion() == C.CMD_RETURN_FORCED) {
      return C.CMD_RETURN_FORCED;
    }
  }

        Structured approach: C([3])+CMD([313]4)+RETURN([185]20211814)+FORCED([61]518354)
